blogPost.excerpt:
Minecraft, But It's 2D... This was super cool! 
We were able to experience Minecraft in a way never seen before!

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @sapnap
➽ Twitch - @sapnap
➽ Instagram - @sapnapinsta

Dream: @Dream 
George: @GeorgeNotFound

This is a Minecraft 1.16 Mod that allows us to see Minecraft from the 2D perspective! This was super cool and a new way to experience the game! Even though this may have seemed easy, this challenge was actually difficult! Will we be able to beat the game? This was a lot of fun and I love doing challenges like this with my friends.
